                            <comment id="13290816" author="lancenorskog" created="Thu, 7 Jun 2012 06:55:55 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Prints Accuracy and Reliability stats, plus standard deviation of reliability.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Accuracy = &quot;Producer Accuracy&quot;, includes unclassified results.&lt;br/&gt;
Reliability = &quot;User Accuracy&quot;, does not include unclassified results.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
